---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const CWS_URL = 'https://chromewebstore.google.com/detail/hbaodafglfcggljhdefilahgcpipcckg';
---

<Layout title="About — Promptory" description="Why we built Promptory — a private, local-first AI prompt manager for power users.">

  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="page-label">About</div>
      <h1>Built for people who take AI seriously.</h1>
      <p class="lead">Promptory started as a personal frustration — and turned into the tool we wished existed.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="content">

    <div class="story">
      <p>
        If you use AI tools every day, you know the feeling: you write a brilliant prompt,
        get a great result, close the tab — and spend the next week trying to remember
        how you phrased it. You rewrite it from scratch. It's never quite as good.
      </p>
      <p>
        That's the problem Promptory solves. It runs quietly in the background, capturing
        every prompt you send across ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Perplexity, Grok, and Copilot.
        No copy-pasting. No manual saving. Just open the side panel when you need something,
        and it's there.
      </p>
      <p>
        We built Promptory to be fast, invisible, and genuinely useful — the kind of tool that
        gets out of your way and just works.
      </p>
    </div>

    <h2>What we believe</h2>
    <div class="values">
      {[
        { icon: '⚡', title: 'Zero friction', body: 'Tools that require manual effort don\'t get used. Promptory is invisible until you need it — then it\'s instantly there.' },
        { icon: '🌐', title: 'Platform agnostic', body: 'We don\'t pick favorites. Promptory works across all major AI platforms, equally.' },
      ].map(v => (
        <div class="value-card">
          <div class="icon">{v.icon}</div>
          <h3>{v.title}</h3>
          <p>{v.body}</p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <h2>The roadmap</h2>
    <div class="story">
      <p>Promptory v1 is focused on doing the core job reliably. What's next:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Folder organization — group prompts into projects or workflows</li>
        <li>Prompt result comparison — compare responses to the same prompt across different AI platforms side by side</li>
        <li>Chat links — jump back to the original conversation directly from any saved prompt</li>
        <li>Browser sync — optional encrypted sync across your own devices</li>
        <li>Community library — browse high-quality prompts shared by the community (opt-in)</li>
        <li>Firefox support</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Have a feature request? Email <a href="mailto:info@promptory.chat">info@promptory.chat</a> — we read every message.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="cta-box">
      <h2>Try it for free</h2>
      <p>No account. No setup. Works in 30 seconds.</p>
      <a href={CWS_URL} target="_blank" class="btn-white">Add to Chrome</a>
    </div>

  </div>

</Layout>

<style>
  .page-hero .lead { font-size: 18px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.7; max-width: 580px; margin-top: 12px; }

  .content { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 64px 24px 96px; }

  .story p { font-size: 16px; color: #333; line-height: 1.85; margin-bottom: 20px; }
  .story ul { margin: 12px 0 20px 20px; }
  .story li { font-size: 15px; color: #333; line-height: 1.75; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .story a { color: var(--brand); }
  .story a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  .story strong { font-weight: 600; color: var(--text); }

  h2 { font-size: 26px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.5px; margin: 48px 0 20px; }

  .values { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; }
  .value-card { border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; background: var(--bg-soft); }
  .value-card .icon { font-size: 28px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .value-card h3 { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .value-card p { font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.65; }

  .cta-box {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand) 0%, var(--brand-d) 100%);
    border-radius: 16px; padding: 40px; text-align: center; margin-top: 64px; color: #fff;
  }
  .cta-box h2 { color: #fff; margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 24px; letter-spacing: -0.5px; }
  .cta-box p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.82); font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  .btn-white {
    background: #fff; color: var(--brand);
    padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 9px;
    font-size: 14px; font-weight: 700;
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    transition: transform .15s;
  }
  .btn-white:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); }
</style>
